concepts.conceptSummary: The golden fulcrum where small proof creates massive transformation

concepts.name: THE KEYSTONE
concepts.conceptSummary: The one critical element that makes everything else work - with hidden SV
concepts.ohMoment: First glance: golden wedge with flanking lines. Second: 'Those lines would complete an arch...' Third: 'And wait - is that an S and V built into the gold shape?'

concepts.name: THE PIVOT
concepts.conceptSummary: The same element in two states - before and after transformation around proof
concepts.ohMoment: First glance: abstract mark with gold center. Second: 'The left and right are the SAME shape - but one has rotated up...' Third: 'The gold point CAUSED the transformation.'
